    {
        "content": "<p>Hello!</p>\n<p>I don't see mention of the Tier 2 upgrade in Rust 1.82.0 release notes, is it normal? I was wondering if the new toolchain is available or not?</p>\n<p>Thanks <span aria-label=\"pray\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f64f\" role=\"img\" title=\"pray\">:pray:</span></p>",
        "id": 478774747,
        "sender_full_name": "raskyld",
        "timestamp": 1729794045
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Oh it's in the <a href=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/releases/tag/1.82.0\">main release notes</a> but not present in the blog post yeah. But yes <code>wasm32-wasip2</code> is available now</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/releases/tag/1.82.0\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/releases/tag/1.82.0\" title=\"Release Rust 1.82.0 · rust-lang/rust\">Release Rust 1.82.0 · rust-lang/rust</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">Language\n\nDon't make statement nonterminals match pattern nonterminals\nPatterns matching empty types can now be omitted in common cases\nEnforce supertrait outlives obligations when using trait impl...</div></div></div>",
        "id": 478775010,
        "sender_full_name": "Alex Crichton",
        "timestamp": 1729794154
